bounty.aspiring.description: A balanced challenge. Find this weapon in three attempts to complete this bounty flawlessly.
bounty.daily.description: To warm up before moving on to the other tests that Banshee-44 has in store for you. Relax and take your time.
bounty.secret.description: Banshee-44 does not recall providing you with such a bounty. The answer to this mystery may not be here...
bounty.true.description: The ultimate test Banshee-44 has in store for you. You will only have one try to complete this bounty flawlessly.
bounty.unknown.description: An unknown bounty by Banshee-44. What are you up to?
collection.description: Your collection includes the items you have found, as well as the engrams Banshee-44 has given you as rewards for completing bounties.
connection.expired: Bungie may be doing a maintenance or your authentication tokens have exprired
discord.description: Join us on Discord to share your achievements, help improve the Trials of Banshee or just chat.
engrams.description: An engram you obtained by completing a Banshee-44 bounty
eternity.notfound: You are currently at the edge of the universe. The Trials of Banshee-44 is not here. You can return to solar system orbit with the button below.
eternity.xur.message.1: Xur is glad to see that you have received his message.
eternity.xur.message.2: He tells you that the starhorse greatly appreciated your performance in the Trials of Banshee-44.
eternity.xur.message.3: To thank you, Xûr gives you a capsule containing a sod, apparently from a garden in the Last City.
eternity.xur.message.4: "You travel a lot in space. Here's a little something to remind you of solid ground."
eternity.xur.message.5: The capsule contains a switch allowing access to its contents.
eternity.xur.message.6: "Feel free to run your hand through it", continues Xûr, "You can't imagine the benefits it can have on the mind. Especially after traveling the universe for hours."
items.description: An item you got on your journey through the universe that questions your life choices
orbit.connection.detail: You can still play as guest but with limited functionnalities
orbit.title: Trials of Banshee

trials.bounty.reward.no.description: Banshee-44 has a weak memory. If you don't sign in with your Bungie account, he won't remember you came by. Log in to receive engrams and progress to your triumphs.

trials.informations.common: Weapons are the same for all Guardians. Try not to spoil.
